From 03df8c6af4ec4e5d547e9fff46d0710b3c262c58 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Michael Natterer <mitch@gimp.org>
Date: Sun, 10 Nov 2013 00:18:48 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] plug-ins: pass the format's name again in calls to
 gimp_export_image()

and clean up the formatting of the call and the lines around it. Now
we can check the various (disabled) export options for regressions
again by changing a single line in gimp_export_image().
---
